---
layout: stories.njk
title: "English"
description: "Third Place Japan Stories in English — guides to finding your third place in Japan, evaluated by TPJ's 7-axis certification framework."
canonical: "/en/stories/"
lang: "en"
hreflang_ja: "/stories/"
hreflang_en: "/en/stories/"
---

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

  <div class="mb-14" data-aos="fade-up">
    <p class="label mb-4">English</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-light text-dark mb-4">Third Place Japan — English Stories</h1>
    <div class="gold-rule mb-6"></div>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
      Third Place Japan evaluates spaces across Japan using a seven-axis framework.
      These English articles introduce the concept of the third place in a Japanese context.
    </p>
  </div>

  {% set enArticles = collections.articles | selectLang("en") %}

  <div class="space-y-6" data-aos="fade-up">
    {% for post in enArticles %}
    {% set postCat = categories | findCategoryBySlug(post.data.category_slug) %}
    <a href="{{ post.url }}"
       class="group flex items-stretch bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border hover:border-gold shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="shrink-0 w-40 md:w-52 overflow-hidden">
        <img src="{{ post.data.thumbnail }}"
             alt="{{ post.data.title }}"
             class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
             loading="lazy" decoding="async">
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 md:p-6 flex flex-col justify-center min-w-0">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs text-gold border border-gold rounded-full px-3 py-0.5 mb-3 w-fit">
          {% if postCat %}{{ postCat.name_en }}{% elif post.data.category_slug == "about" %}Concept{% else %}Journal{% endif %}
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-base md:text-lg font-light text-dark group-hover:text-gold transition-colors leading-snug mb-2">
          {{ post.data.title }}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed"
           style="display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:2;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden;">
          {{ post.data.description }}
        </p>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="mt-14 pt-10 border-t border-border text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
    <a href="/stories/" class="text-sm text-muted hover:text-gold transition-colors">← 日本語版 TPJ Stories</a>
  </div>

</div>
